'''溫德漢姆錦標賽'''（{{lang-en|Wyndham Championship}}）是美國高爾夫球[[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]的賽事。溫德漢姆錦標賽一半在北卡羅來納州舉行。溫德漢姆錦標賽開始於1938年。在2007年，賽事改為現在的名稱<ref>{{cite news |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/golf/pga/2006-09-29-greensboro-sponsor_x.htm |title=Greensboro PGA Tour event gets new sponsor |newspaper=USA Today |agency=Associated Press |date=September 29, 2006 |accessdate=2016-02-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304232455/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/golf/pga/2006-09-29-greensboro-sponsor_x.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年溫德漢姆錦標賽的獎金是540萬美元，冠軍獎金97.2萬美元<ref>{{cite news |title=Golf Glance |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/golf/2015/08/18/golf-glance/31906257/ |accessdate=August 8, 2015 |date=August 18, 2015 |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=USA Today |archive-date=2020-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424143744/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/golf/2015/08/18/golf-glance/31906257/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

